      "author": "willsamadi (Will Samadi)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi all,</p>\n<p>I am very excited to announce the release of my new app “ActionLink”.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000735/actionlink---clientfacing-dashoboards\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Link to marketplace page</a></p>\n<p>To be precise;</p>\n<h2><a name=\"p-225207-problems-it-solves-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-225207-problems-it-solves-1\"></a><strong>Problems it solves:</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Adding clients as guests/viewers gives them access to all the items on the board</li>\n<li>Sharing progress with clients</li>\n<li>Getting feedback from client on certain items</li>\n<li>Having a client dashboard with multiple views (possibly from multiple boards)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a name=\"p-225207-helpful-if-you-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-225207-helpful-if-you-2\"></a><strong>Helpful if you:</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Want your client to see the progress and status of each item <strong>with granular access-control</strong></li>\n<li>Need clients to go through a checklist and <strong>give you their input on certain a list of items</strong></li>\n<li>Need clients to <strong>trigger an automation</strong> via a secure link to confirm, approve or cancel internal processes without seeing your entire board</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a name=\"p-225207-features-coming-soon-by-the-end-of-march-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-225207-features-coming-soon-by-the-end-of-march-3\"></a>Features Coming Soon (by the end of March):</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Support for more column types</li>\n<li>Support for item-based views with automatic link generation (no need to manually create links) to show subitems to client <strong>with permission control</strong></li>\n<li>Categrozied and prettier client dashboard</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a name=\"p-225207-features-in-our-backlog-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-225207-features-in-our-backlog-4\"></a>Features in our backlog:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Branding options for client dashboard</li>\n<li>Custom view types (meeting scheduler, simple trigger button, …)</li>\n<li>Much more! We are very actively developing so let us know what would be great to have</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000735/actionlink---clientfacing-dashoboards\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>Link to marketplace page</strong></a><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <a href=\"https://calendar.app.google/GosHDLGxS4oFnkBJA\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>Book a free demo</strong></a><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <a href=\"https://forms.monday.com/forms/39c1cd7f96c03c8d9abd2a296958508a?r=use1\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>Ask a question by filling our contact form</strong></a></p>\n<p>Very excited to hear your thoughts and comments!</p>"
